Learning Terraform

1. Installation: MAC-OS
-----------------------
  brew tap hashicorp/tap
  brew install terraform 

1.1 Upgrading Terraform
-----------------------
  brew upgrade hashicorp/tap/terraform

1.2 Verify the installation
---------------------------
  terraform -help

1.2.1 Add any sub-command to terraform -help to learn more about what it does:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  terraform -help plan


